<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>With the current unreleased Zend_View_Helper_Placeholder_Container_Abstract, it is possible to set and append data, but not prepend. I first realized this problem when I wanted to prepend a string with the HeadTitle view helper.</p>

    </div>
