        <div class="body">
            <p>This method would do the trick, but I'm sure something more space-efficient could be done:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
public function prepend($value) {
    $values = $this-&gt;getArrayCopy();

    array_unshift($values, $value);

    $this-&gt;exchangeArray($values);
}
</code></pre>

